  "instructions": [
    "Heat olive oil in a pan over medium heat.",
    "Add shallots and minced garlic, sauté for about 2 minutes until fragrant.",
    "Fold in cooked quinoa and cook for another minute to incorporate flavors.",
    "Add sliced carrots and bell peppers, tossing well with the mixture.",
    "Mix in soy sauce, fish sauce, lemon juice, salt, and pepper. Stir until combined.",
    "Reduce heat to low and simmer for about 10 minutes or until vegetables are tender.",
    "Serve hot as a side dish or over rice for a full meal."
